ActBudget Implementation Act, 2018, No. 2
SubjectOrder Fixing April 1, 2025 as the Day on Which Certain Provisions of the Budget Implementation Act, 2018, No. 2 Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing April 1, 2025 as the day on which Sections 215 to 217, 219, 221 to 223 and 225 to 228 under subsection 242(2) of the BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2018, NO. 2, COME INTO FORCE in order to amend the Trademarks Regulations.
